 style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Denzel\nWashington &nbsp;&nbsp;Forest Whitaker<br>\nNate Parker &nbsp;&nbsp;Jurnee Smollett &nbsp;&nbsp;Denzel Whitaker<br>\nJohn Heard </span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>and</span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> Kimberly\nElise<br>\n</span><span style='font-size:4.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>screenplay\nby</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> </span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Robert\nEisele</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:4.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>story\nby</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> </span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Robert\nEisele</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> </span><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>&amp;</span><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> </span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Jeffrey\nPorro</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:4.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>directed\nby</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> </span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Denzel\nWashington</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:17.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Wednesday,\nDecember 19, 2007</span><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><b><span style='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>6:30-7:30pm</span></b><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> Cocktails </span><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>&amp;</span><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> Hors d&#8217; oeuvres Reception</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>The Ziegfeld Theater Lobby</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>7:30pm</span></b><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> Screening</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>The Ziegfeld Theater<br>\n141 West 54th Street<br>\n</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>(</span><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>between </span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>6th Avenue</span><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> and</span><span\nstyle='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'> Broadway)</span><span\nstyle='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n<br>\n</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>peggy@peggysiegal.com\nor 212-935-6700<br>\nthis invitation is non-transferable</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:4.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:4.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>Believe\nin the power of words.<br>\n</span><span style='font-size:5.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>From\ntwo-time Academy Award winner Denzel Washington and an ensemble cast lead by Washington\nthat includes Academy Award winner Forest Whitaker, comes THE GREAT DEBATERS.\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Inspired by a true story, &nbsp;THE GREAT DEBATERS chronicles the\njourney of Professor Melvin Tolson (Denzel &nbsp;Washington), a brilliant but\nvolatile debate team coach who uses the &nbsp;power of words to shape a group\nof underdog students from a small African American college in the deep south\ninto a historically elite &nbsp;debate team. A controversial figure, Professor\nTolson challenged the &nbsp;social mores of the time and was under constant\nfire for his unconventional and ferocious teaching methods as well as his\nradical political views.<br>\n</span><span style='font-size:5.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'><br>\n</span><span style='font-size:9.0pt;font-family:\"Century Gothic\",\"sans-serif\"'>In\ntheir pursuit for excellence, Tolson's debate team receives a groundbreaking\ninvitation to debate Harvard University's championship team &nbsp;The film is\ndirected by Denzel Washington and stars Washington, &nbsp;Forest Whitaker,\nJurnee Smollett, Nate Parker, Denzel Whitaker, and &nbsp;Kimberly Elise.\n&quot;The Great Debaters&quot; was written by Robert Eisele and produced by\nTodd Black, Kate Forte, Oprah Winfrey and Joe &nbsp;Roth. &nbsp;Presented by\nThe Weinstein Company, &quot;The Great Debaters,&quot; will &nbsp;be released\nby MGM on December 25th.</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"'>&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellpadding=0 width=\"100%\"\n style='width:100.0%;background:white'>\n <tr>\n  <td style='padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt'>\n  <div align=center>\n  <table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellpadding=0 width=595\n   style='width:446.25pt;background:white'>\n   <tr>\n    <td style='padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt'>\n    <p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:7.5pt;font-family:\"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"'><a\n    href=\"http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=un&amp;v=0016DNjNiidDhR5-hLIXFRFoKynI9wK9QlvYoJKQ1f6JA_-jYKRQidsLMJLW9yIfjsbGrEHaeT-2jVtQoUhUg8zHw%3D%3D\"\n    target=\"_blank\"><span style='text-decoration:none'><img border=0\n    id=\"_x0000_i1026\"\n    src=\"http://img.constantcontact.com/letters/images/safe_unsubscribe_logo.gif\"></span></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <div>\n    <p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:7.5pt;font-family:\"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"'>This\n    email was sent to lesley@nysgllc.com, by <a\n    href=\"mailto:peggy@peggysiegal.com\">peggy@peggysiegal.com</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n    <p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:7.5pt;font-family:\"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"'><a\n    href=\"http://visitor.constantcontact.com/d.jsp?p=oo&amp;v=0016DNjNiidDhR5-hLIXFRFoKynI9wK9QlvYoJKQ1f6JA_-jYKRQidsLMJLW9yIfjsbGrEHaeT-2jVtQoUhUg8zHw%3D%3D\"\n    ta